quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  2,270,Any charity vos dedit charitable pledge vos fulfill DEUS est fully aware thereof! Prout pro wicked they non habet helpers
  2,271,Vos declare tuus charities they est adhuc bonus! Vos keep them anonymous dedit them poor est bonus vos remits multus de tuus sins DEUS EST fully Cognizant DE everything VOS PERFECIT
  2,272,Vos non est responsible pro guiding anyone. DEUS est UNUS UNUS guides whoever chooses guided Any charity vos dedit est tuus suus bonus Any charity vos dedit est DEUS. Any charity vos dedit repaid vos parvus injustice
  2,273,Charity iit poor suffering causa DEUS ac non emigrate! unaware maius think they est rich due to their dignity. Vos recognize them certain signum; they nunquam beg people persistently. Whatever charity vos dedit DEUS est fully aware thereof
  2,274,Those dedit charity nox feria secretly publicly receive their recompense their Dominus; they habet nihil fear nor testimentum they grieve